<FIRST>u f BC-BoardofTrade Close   12-09 0215</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Board of Trade, Close,0225</SECOND>
<HEAD>Grain, Soybean Futures Finish Mixed</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CHICAGO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
