<HEAD>New Security Aimed at Unbundling Stock Value</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-New Security</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 Here is a capsule description of an unbundled stock unit, a new type of security developed by <ORGANIZATION> Shearson </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Lehman </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Hutton </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION>. Four major companies _ <ORGANIZATION> American </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Express </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION>, <PERSON> Sara </PERSON> <PERSON> Lee </PERSON> <ORGANIZATION> Corp. </ORGANIZATION>, <ORGANIZATION> Pfizer </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION> and <ORGANIZATION> Dow </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Chemical </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Co. </ORGANIZATION> _ have announced plans, subject to federal review, to exchange up to $ 5.6 billion of their stock for unbundled stock units The new securities consist of: _ A 30-year bond that pays interest equal to the current stock dividend and carrying a face value payable in 2019 higher than the current stock price Under the preliminary proposal, for instance, <ORGANIZATION> American </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Express </ORGANIZATION>'s bond would pay 84 cents a year in interest and have a face value of $ 75 <ORGANIZATION> American </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Express </ORGANIZATION> stock was trading at $ 26.87 -LCB- the last trading day before the proposal. _ A share of preferred stock that will entitle the holder to any dividends declared by the company in excess of the current dividend For <ORGANIZATION> American </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Express </ORGANIZATION>, that would be anything above 84 cents a year. The preferred share could also be redeemed in 2019 for a nominal price expected to be $ 2. _ A stock appreciation certificate that will give the holder the right to purchase for cash a share of the company's stock in 2019 for the principal amount of the bond plus the preferred share In the <ORGANIZATION> American </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Express </ORGANIZATION> example, that would be $ 77. It is expected that, subject to appropriate approvals, the unbundled stock unit, each of its parts and a security that combines the preferred share and the stock appreciation certificate would be traded on the <ORGANIZATION> New </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> York </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Stock </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Exchange </ORGANIZATION>, just as the company's stock.
</TEXT>
